CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 6, 1946, pg. 25, reads: "YMCA Tournament Champions - Upper left: The 'Y' Vets are shown receiving the beautiful trophy given by the Pittsburgh Courier for the senior title. They are, left to right: Coach Carson, Adams, Ford, Myers, Fowler, Pollard, Ches Washington making the presentation, Atkins, Lewis, and Ritter... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Chester "Ches" Washington presenting Center Avenue YMCA championship basketball trophy to Ernest Myers, surrounded by YMCA Vets team coach Carson and players Adams, Ford, Fowler, Pollard, Atkins, Lewis, and Ritter
